Package: SveltePlots
Type: Package
Version: 0.1.0
Title: A Wrapper for a Svelte Custom Web Component
Authors@R: 
  person("Pascal", "Schmidt", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "pascal.sfu@gmail.com")
Author: Pascal Schmidt [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Pascal Schmidt <pascal.sfu@gmail.com>
Description: SveltePlots is an interactive charting library designed to easily produce SVG-based visualizations using R. 
  It leverages Svelte's reactive state management to eliminate the need for Shiny's renderUI, insertUI, removeUI, and proxy functions, 
  resulting in a more streamlined and efficient workflow for building dynamic plots. 
URL: https://github.com/Pascal-Schmidt/SveltePlots, https://pascal-schmidt.github.io/SveltePlots/
